title: Full Show (LeBron and Lakers lose to Warriors 123-109, Marcus Smart and Joel Embiid have dust-up, Eagles favored in every game)
description:
00:00 Lakers fall to Warriors 123-109; LeBron has 31 pts
23:36 Expect the Cowboys offense to skyrocket when Dak returns?
51:22 Pete Carroll, John Harbaugh, Frank Reich and Andy Reid call on owners to "make progress" hiring Black coaches
1:03:49 Marcus Smart and Joel Embiid have dust-up in Celtics 126-117 win over Sixers
1:14:17 Does last night show GSW can move on from Draymond-Pool altercation?
1:25:11 Aaron Rodgers wants to simplify Green Bay's offense
1:39:47 KD defends Russ: "Now you're making him the butt of your jokes"
1:49:31 Will the Eagles be the first undefeated team since the 1972 Dolphins?
1:54:06 Marshawn Lynch says Russell Wilson alienates his teammates
